    "content": "Number of deactivating group of the following is\n\n$$\n-\\mathrm{Cl},-\\mathrm{SO}_3 \\mathrm{H},-\\mathrm{OH},-\\mathrm{NHC}_2 \\mathrm{H}_5,-\\mathrm{COOCH}_3,-\\mathrm{CH}_3\n$$\n\n",
