    "answer": null,
    "explanation": "<p> The electron withdrawing group increases the basicity while electron donating group decreases the basicity. So , the correct order is</p>\n<p>$$ B&gt;A&gt;C $$</p>\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m8qailp7/20af5087-c874-4686-9c43-adf23aa5b116/a42222b0-0a74-11f0-93a1-adbaa87ebf49/file-jaoe38c1m8qailp8.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m8qailp7/20af5087-c874-4686-9c43-adf23aa5b116/a42222b0-0a74-11f0-93a1-adbaa87ebf49/file-jaoe38c1m8qailp8.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"AP EAPCET 2024 - 21th May Morning Shift Chemistry - General Organic Chemistry Question 7 English Explanation\">",
