    "correct_options": [
      "C"
    ],
    "answer": null,
    "explanation": "<p>The following three compound shows negative resonance $(-R)$ effect when attached to conjugate system. $A \\rightarrow$ formyl, $D \\rightarrow$ cyano, $E \\rightarrow$ nitro. The negative resonance effect occurs when the groups withdraw the electrons from other molecules by delocalisation process.</p>",
