    "direction": null,
    "content": "<p>The following effect is known as</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1ly461kd4/ab4efd88-3bdf-4bd2-a39e-68dad6dc75d0/bdc0dd80-384f-11ef-91ff-bf539f05d7ac/file-jaoe38c1ly461kd5.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1ly461kd4/ab4efd88-3bdf-4bd2-a39e-68dad6dc75d0/bdc0dd80-384f-11ef-91ff-bf539f05d7ac/file-jaoe38c1ly461kd5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"AP EAPCET 2021 - 19th August Morning Shift Chemistry - General Organic Chemistry Question 19 English\"></p>",
